@startuml sds-layered
title Layered Architecture - Reading Book App
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam ArrowColor #333333
skinparam packageBorderColor #333333

rectangle "Presentation (UI)\nReact screens, gestures, theme tokens, Invisible UI" as P #E3F2FD
rectangle "Application (Use cases)\nImportBook, OpenReader, SaveProgress, AddHighlight..." as A #FFF3CD
rectangle "Domain (shared model & rules)\nBook, Location, Highlight, Note, Overlay invariants" as D #E8F5E9
rectangle "Infrastructure (adapters & technical services)\nSQLite/FTS5, FileStore, DocumentAdapters, IPC, AI stub" as I #FCE4EC

P -down-> A : depends
A -down-> D : depends
I .up.> A : implements ports
I .up.> D : implements ports

note right of P
  Quy tac: chi phu thuoc xuong duoi.
  Domain khong import React / Electron / SQLite.
end note

@enduml
